            WSO2 AD 4.5.1 stores and retrieves information on your browser using cookies. Some cookies allow a user to
            log in to the system and maintain sessions. Some cookies are simply used to give you a more personalised
            web experience and these cookies cannot be used to personally identify you or your activities.
        </p>
        <p>
            This cookie policy is part of the WSO2 AD 4.5.1 <a href="{{@contextPath}}/privacy-policy">Privacy
